Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:14.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:15.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:18.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:23.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:26.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:34.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:40.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:59.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:13.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:15.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.88,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy85\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(447.167,120.389)}The Monstrous Bird
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.88,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy80\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(567.167,727.389)}Pranodon Attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:29.26,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen closely,\Nall you young ladies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:33.98,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go falling\Nfor a mountain man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:37.14,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he gets lost in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:40.37,Default Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll end up a young widow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.71,0:01:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish Hayato, Taki,\Nand Mika could have come with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira's father will be\Nback from America soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be busy with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad to get to see\Nyour father again after a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he said he'd\Nbuy me a toy rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:01:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go around littering just\Nbecause we're out in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What a hopeless kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's a tunnel doing\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it lead to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let us begin the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:13.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker implanted a receiver\Ncapsule into Emi's ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can now control this girl\Nwith the radio waves I emit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi! Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where she\Ncould have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been, Emi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We found her.\NThat's what matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the fun will begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to me. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get\Nfor refusing my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm going mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,From this moment forward,\Nyou will do as I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:06:00.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Doctor Namikawa,\Na world leader in rocketry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:03.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,was returning to Japan following\Na two-year joint research project
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:12.97,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H2804A4&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Welcome Home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:19.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taki, on orders from the FBI\Nin case something went wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,was assigned to guard\NDoctor Namikawa in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hayato would also be there,\Nin his role as a photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:29.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to take pictures\Nof Doctor Namikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a brilliant scholar\Nlike Doctor Namikawa back in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,will prove detrimental\Nto our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn on the TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch now, Ichimonji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You will kill the\Ndoctor yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've rigged Ichimonji's camera
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to fire a miniature rocket\Nwhen he presses the shutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,An assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He was caught in the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't talk him out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to you, he's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency,\Nso I might as well tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... you're FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your assassination of Doctor Namikawa\Nappears to have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A regrettable coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ichimonji cannot meddle\Nfrom within a jail cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take advantage of the situation\Nand move the plan forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile,\Nat the Namikawa home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Light injuries to the left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was pretty calm about\Nthe whole incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told them that\Nthis morning's incident
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,was just a malfunctioning\Nflashbulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi, is that you? \NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi, what's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown\Nyourselves, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the force of my wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you, cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:59.77,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We've planted a receiver\Ncapsule in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Pranodon will\Ncontrol your every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato... where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A policeman came by earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato... where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- A policeman?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is,\Nright after the police released you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He made it sound like\Nyou were a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki was kidnapped by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- By Shocker?\N- Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones\Nbehind all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have swapped my\Ncamera, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would they\Nbe so circuitous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not just attack\NDoctor Namikawa directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to both kill him,\Nand frame me for the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NThat does sound like Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why Taki was taken, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me. Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobei and the\Nothers are worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They says you've been acting\Nstrange since you went hiking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You went missing in the mountains\Nfor an hour, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to\Nyou during that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible...\Nyou ran into some kind of winged creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You were under\NShocker's control!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who\Nswapped my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Emi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I've heard you're the\NFBI's greatest marksman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To test it,\Nsee if you can hit those targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But can you pull the trigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot refuse me.\NDo you see that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, stand! Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Point that rifle at the target
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plan is now\Nall but complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Give this man his next\Nmission assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, this man will\Nbe your next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Namikawa is heading for Mount\NIkuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You will set an ambush\Nfor him on the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill him with that rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:33.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Doctor Namikawa and\NAkira were leaving the city
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:35.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,on a drive to Mount Ikuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:43.74,Italics,,0,0,0,,Doctor Namikawa's car is heading for\NIkuta Driveway across Route 246,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:47.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,traveling at 60\Nkilometers per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:54.43,Italics,,0,0,0,,His car will reach the\Nsniping point in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something\Nstrange in her ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you look a little deeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This capsule was inserted right\Nnext to her tympanic membrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a receiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A receiver?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,An extremely delicate receiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But what in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, Doctor Namikawa has just\Nentered Ikuta Driveway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He will reach the sniping\Npoint in seven minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Six minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Namikawa's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniping point...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Namikawa has five\Nminutes left to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to exploit Taki, Shocker...\Nnow you must pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... witness my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Pranodon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not entirely sure what\NI was doing back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here! I don't know\Nhow to apologize to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\NIt's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- It was this.\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This receiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad Doctor Namikawa\Nis all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A young man sent\Nthis for the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't give his\Nname, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.31,0:22:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is for Akira\Nfrom Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so cool! Really neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:22:58.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider,\NIchimonji Hayato,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:23:02.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,managed to protect Doctor Namikawa\Nfrom Shocker's evil scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:04.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But what will they\Nsend after him next?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:07.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Don't let them beat\Nyou, our Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:10.80,Cont,,0,60,160,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:13.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:16.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the graveyard\Nmonster Kabibinga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:23.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He seeks to use young twins to spread\NOperation: Mold everywhere in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:25.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:31.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Graveyard Monster Kabibinga."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.19,0:23:31.11,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs130\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(470.167,715.389)}Graveyard Monster Kabibinga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:40.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:43.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:48.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:50.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:52.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:54.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.57,0:23:56.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:04.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:07.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.71,0:24:11.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:15.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Bird\NPranodon Attacks